        <abstract> 
<p>H. M. S. <hi rend="italic">Nassau</hi>, surveying Magellan Straits, has found fossils at Gallegos River. They have been sent to THH by R. O. Cunningham [naturalist of H. M. S. <hi rend="italic">Nassau</hi>]. Skull of entirely new ungulate mammal.</p> 
